maintain cell regulation or differentiation.

21:48.223 --> 21:49.682
It's impossible.

21:50.392 --> 21:51.600
TERMINATOR:
Possible.

21:56.857 --> 21:58.691
Woo was wrong.

22:01.486 --> 22:03.029
Thomason was wrong.

22:03.196 --> 22:06.157
