She's just trying to get attention.

38:17.044 --> 38:18.545
-Jump!
-Dude, come on.

38:18.713 --> 38:19.879
WOMAN 2:
You guys are so mean.

38:20.047 --> 38:23.842
CAMERON: That's my new friend.
The crying one from the bathroom.

38:26.721 --> 38:28.138
When?

38:28.848 --> 38:31.725
Two hours, three minutes ago.
Four minutes ago.

38:31.892 --> 38:33.310
WOMAN 3:
She just wants the attention.

38:33.477 --> 38:37.063
She's upset.
Her parents are gonna kill her.

38:39.025 --> 38:41.234
Did you do anything to her?

38:42.320 --> 38:44.988
I tried to give her a tight present.

38:53.873 --> 38:56.041
-We gotta help her. Now.
-No.

38:56.500 --> 38:57.584
I'm going up there.

39:00.004 --> 39:03.590
-Let me go. I order you to let me go.
-Don't be a freak.

39:03.758 --> 39:05.759
ALL:
Whoa.

39:07.762 --> 39:09.262
[ALL GASPING AND SHOUTING]

39:10.890 --> 39:12.265
We gotta go. Now.

39:21.400 --> 39:25.945
I could have done something.
I was right there.

39:26.364 --> 39:28.114
Maybe.

39:28.616 --> 39:30.575
Come on, Mom.

39:31.744 --> 39:35.455
John, people who wanna
take their own lives, this girl...

39:35.623 --> 39:38.208
...if they're serious about it,
they'll find a way.

39:38.376 --> 39:40.543
You didn't see her.

39:41.253 --> 39:44.047
If you'd have seen her,
you wouldn't be talking like this.

39:44.215 --> 39:46.299
And what were you gonna do,
be a hero?

39:47.551 --> 39:50.595
Get your name in the papers?
Your face?

39:51.305 --> 39:55.225
Isn't that what I'm supposed to be?
A hero? Isn't that who I am?

39:56.268 --> 39:59.229
If it's just gonna sit inside me,
just gonna sit in my gut...

39:59.397 --> 40:02.816
...then what are we doing?
What's the point?

40:03.067 --> 40:06.361
Why not just give it to them
if we're gonna act like them?

40:13.619 --> 40:15.870
I don't know how to help him.

40:19.667 --> 40:21.126
Andy Goode must be killed.

40:24.338 --> 40:26.756
[POLICE RADIO CHATTER]

41:07.923 --> 41:09.174
Took his eyes, James.

41:11.552 --> 41:13.428
They took his freaking eyes.

41:27.568 --> 41:29.194
SARAH [VOICE-OVER]:
On July 16th, 1945...

41:29.361 --> 41:32.739
...in the mountains outside of
Los Alamos, New Mexico...

41:32.907 --> 41:36.242
...the world's first atomic bomb
exploded.

41:36.702 --> 41:39.204
A white light pierced the sky
with such intensity...

41:39.371 --> 41:43.708
...that a blind girl claimed to see
the flash from a hundred miles away.

41:43.876 --> 41:45.502
After witnessing the explosion...

41:45.669 --> 41:48.838
...J. Robert Oppenheimer quoted
a fragment of the Bhagavad-Gita...

41:49.006 --> 41:54.093
...declaring, "I am become death,
the destroyer of worlds."

41:54.762 --> 41:57.847
[DISTANT SIRENS WAILING]

41:58.057 --> 42:01.100
His colleague, Ken Bainbridge,
put it another way...

42:01.268 --> 42:03.770
...when he leaned close to Oppenheimer
and whispered:

42:03.938 --> 42:06.898
"Now we are all sons of bitches."

43:02.955 --> 43:06.416
Now we are all sons of bitches.
